surf_ezclap

surf_ezclap is a tier 3 map with 5 stages. Includes 1 bonus. 

This map is intended to be played on 66 tick with sv_accelerate 5, sv_airaccelerate 150 and 3500 maxvelocity.  Map includes start- and end zones for server owners.

http://steamcommunity.com/id/sjomlee
